INSERT INTO `cms_news` VALUES ('16', 'COTW #1', 'party.png', 'Gambling Galore', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>COTW #1!</strong></h2>\r\n<h3>Welcome to the first week of&nbsp;<strong>Casino of the Week</strong>! Each week, players will build a casino to show off their wonderful stacks to be judged! As prizes, the top&nbsp;<strong>3 best built</strong>&nbsp;casinos will be awarded with various prizes! Think you\'ve got the eye for design? Test your stacking skills this week!</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>PLEASE NOTE: In order to participate in any COTW competition you will have to put \'COTW #(Whatever week this cotw is; for example \"COTW #1\")\' as the room name or your rooms will not be judged! Also, please be original. You may turn to google for some inspiration, but any rooms copied directly from google will be disqualified. These competitions are not for you to steal someone else\'s work entirely and call it your own.</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2><strong>COTW</strong><strong>&nbsp;#1</strong></h2>\r\n<p>There\'s typically no theme for COTW as everyone likes to design differently, but I want to be a little different.</p>\r\n<p><strong>The Theme for this first week is.... Dance Party!</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Few Rules:</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>No copying rooms from google</strong></li>\r\n<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>No using the same room/design for more than one week.</strong></li>\r\n<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>The room must be finished before the deadline.</strong></li>\r\n<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>Do not clear/pickall your room till after the news article has been posted to ensure that the judges saw your room!</strong></li>\r\n<li style=\"padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>Your room should be built around the dice, meaning do not just build a nice room, throw in some dice, and call it a casino!</strong></li>\r\n<li style=\"padding-